Vue 3's \`<Teleport to=\"#target\">\` for rendering content outside the component's DOM hierarchy is not implemented. Essential for modals, tooltips, and overlays.

```html
<template>
  <Teleport to='body'>
    <div class=\"modal\">...</div>
  </Teleport>
</template>
```